  m_text: 'LITERALLY ALL MEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEE


    aside from some people who gave
    me help, including but not limited to:

    apoorv for help with game and systems
    design

    jao for inspiring me to make this damn thing

    the rest of GD68
    for listening to me when i talked about this in the chat

    you, for testing
    this! thank you in advance for your feedback.

'
